value.0: Even the most frugal of mercenaries know they need at least some form of protection from the rigors of combat, although suits of this type are recommended for light skirmishes only.

There are a variety of different kinds of armor intended to defend against the harsh enviroments of space, deflect the impact of blaster bolts and protect versus all types of damage that can be found on a battlefield. These suits are usually built in with a personal shield generator.
This area can be conquered by holding the area around this object for a long enough time period
